      <h1>Dryer Repair Cost in Los Angeles</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Labor rates by repair type &mdash; parts quoted separately after diagnosis. A clogged vent is the most common dryer problem in LA and often costs less than you think to fix.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="btn-red">&#9990; (424) 325-0520</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn-outline">Book Online</a>
